metadata.name: Crazy Jane
metadata.description:
This is a story about a very ordinary girl who studied well at school and was an exemplary girl. But then her life changes abruptly. She understands that everything she was taught as a child does not work in reality.
She gives up everything and goes to the big city, finds new friends, implements new projects. 
She almost does not want to sleep, because energy is bubbling in her! Look how bright and shiny it is around! It is she who sparkles! 
She's very smart. She has 1000 ideas and many possibilities in her head. She decides to act independently and clearly goes according to the planned plan. At the same time, she does not forget to relax with friends! 
Now she goes through life with a positive attitude. Only forward, only positive, only new achievements!
